# ‚ï∞‚îÄ> Received from stream: Post #2 - ...
#üîÑ Fetching URL #3: https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts/3
# ‚ï∞‚îÄ> Received from stream: Post #3 - ...
#
#‚úÖ All HTTP requests completed!

